   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Send 20 Orphans to School-Donate Goats in Cameroon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">BERUDA&apos;s Orphan Education Through Goats project provides a sustainable means for orphans to pay school fees in Fundong, NW Cameroon. It targets 20 primary school-aged orphans not currently attending school by donating goats for breeding and sale at market. Your one-time donation is enough to fund an orphan&apos;s entire education. BERUDA is a grassroots charity that works to eradicate poverty and raise living standards in its communities through sustainable income-generating initiatives.</narrative>
  </description>
